
index for PLAY items

These commands (and help files on commands) concerning playing chess matches
on this server:

   abort             draw              open              resign
   accept            flag              pause             switch
   adjourn           flip              partner           takeback
   assess            match             pending           time
   boards            moretime          promote           unpause
   decline           noplay            refresh           withdraw

Other, informative files (not commands) that are relevant:

   abuser            computers         intro_playing     teamgames
   adjournments      formula           lag               timeseal
   adjudication      glicko            lightning         untimed
   blindfold         interfaces        standard          variables
   blitz             intro_moving      team              wild

Type "help TOPIC" in order to read them.

